600
00:38:12,105 --> 00:38:13,535
You prepared it so carefully.

601
00:38:13,781 --> 00:38:14,868
You should keep it for yourself.

602
00:38:15,784 --> 00:38:17,305
I didn’t want Madam Noi to choke on it

603
00:38:17,313 --> 00:38:18,868
but she’s full now.

604
00:38:20,043 --> 00:38:21,234
The watermelon is for the cat?

605
00:38:21,842 --> 00:38:23,139
Just take it.

606
00:38:23,156 --> 00:38:26,634
There are no separate varieties for humans and cats to eat.

607
00:38:28,135 --> 00:38:29,271
Take it.

608
00:38:29,603 --> 00:38:31,339
At least it’s more refreshing than eating only carbs.

609
00:38:39,213 --> 00:38:39,936
Here.

610
00:38:40,133 --> 00:38:41,533
